Titolo: Necrobarista

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Necrobarista is a 2020 visual novel game developed by Australian development studio Route 59. The player follows a cast of characters around a Melbourne back-alley coffeehouse staffed by necromancers, named the 'Terminal'. In the Terminal, the souls of the recently departed are given a final 24 hours to reside in the world alongside the living. The game was released on July 17, 2020 for macOS and iOS via Apple Arcade, and July 22, 2020 for Microsoft Windows. Necrobarista - Final Pour was released on August 11, 2021 for Nintendo Switch. The game is also scheduled to release at a later date for PlayStation 4.